      "The order search full table scan is caused by a missing index on customer_id, not by a complex query that cannot use an index",
      "The workload is read-heavy (typical for order/delivery systems — ~80% reads, 20% writes)",
      "The system runs on cloud infrastructure where disk expansion and replica provisioning are operational tasks, not hardware procurement",
      "PostgreSQL version is 12+ (required for declarative partitioning)",
